<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 06:14:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国2月份工厂活动可能连续第五个月收缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-feb-factory-activity-likely-contracted-fifth-month-2024-02-29/</link><description>路透周四的一项民意调查显示，中国2月份制造业活动可能连续第五个月萎缩，由于工厂主在国内外争取订单而苦苦挣扎，这可能会加剧要求采取进一步刺激措施的呼声。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 05:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-feb-factory-activity-likely-contracted-fifth-month-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>WTA综述：中国组合晋级ATX公开赛四分之一决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/wta-roundup-chinese-duo-heads-atx-open-quarterfinals-2024-02-29/</link><description>周三，在德克萨斯州奥斯汀举行的 ATX 公开赛第二轮比赛中，中国八号种子袁悦和同胞王亚凡双双横扫对手。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 04:19:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/wta-roundup-chinese-duo-heads-atx-open-quarterfinals-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>美元为美国通胀数据做好准备，日元因日本央行言论而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-braces-us-inflation-reading-yen-gains-boj-comments-2024-02-29/</link><description>美元周四保持坚挺，美国通胀数据可能会影响利率前景，而日元则在日本央行官员暗示需要退出超宽松政策后站稳脚跟。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 04:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-braces-us-inflation-reading-yen-gains-boj-comments-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>在微妙的中国戏中，利洁时转向直播销售安全套</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/delicate-china-play-reckitt-turns-livestreaming-sell-condoms-2024-02-29/</link><description>杜蕾斯母公司利洁时希望中国消费者对直播购物的喜爱也能延伸到安全套的购买上，但该公司在寻求扩大其在价值超过 50 亿美元的安全套市场中的份额时，将不得不采取“微妙的路线”。 。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 04:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/delicate-china-play-reckitt-turns-livestreaming-sell-condoms-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>呼吁澳大利亚间谍头子公布“出卖”的前政治家的名字</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/calls-australian-spy-chief-name-ex-politician-who-sold-out-2024-02-29/</link><description>澳大利亚间谍局长周四面临要求点名这位前政治家的指控，他称这位前政客“出卖”给了外国情报机构，堪培拉前驻美国大使表示，除非查明此人的身份，否则这可能“可能抹黑所有人”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 04:03:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/calls-australian-spy-chief-name-ex-politician-who-sold-out-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国兴趣减弱，亚洲对冲基金发行数量降至 14 年来的最低水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asia-hedge-fund-launches-drop-lowest-number-14-years-china-interest-wanes-2024-02-29/</link><description>数据提供商 Preqin 表示，去年亚洲仅推出 62 只新对冲基金，为 2009 年以来数量最低，且专注于中国的基金仅 15 只。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 03:52:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asia-hedge-fund-launches-drop-lowest-number-14-years-china-interest-wanes-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市在美国通胀数据公布前大幅下挫；日元上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-29/</link><description>周四亚洲股市大多走软，而在重要的美国通胀数据公布之前，美元和美国国债基本保持稳定，这些数据可能为美联储何时降息提供新线索。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 03:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>南华早报报道，澳大利亚邀请中国王毅下个月访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-invites-chinas-wang-yi-visit-next-month-scmp-report-2024-02-29/</link><description>《南华早报》周四援引消息人士的话称，澳大利亚已邀请中国外交部长王毅于 3 月下旬访问，就贸易、安全等领域进行讨论。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 03:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-invites-chinas-wang-yi-visit-next-month-scmp-report-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>财政部长称中国向巴基斯坦提供超过20亿美元贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-rolls-over-2-bln-loan-pakistan-finance-minister-says-2024-02-29/</link><description>看守财政部长沙姆沙德·阿赫塔尔周四在回应路透社时证实，中国已向巴基斯坦提供了 20 亿美元贷款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 02:39:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-rolls-over-2-bln-loan-pakistan-finance-minister-says-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜金正恩在不平等加剧的情况下寻求农村地区的“产业革命”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-seeks-industry-revolution-rural-areas-amid-widening-inequality-2024-02-29/</link><description>官方媒体朝中社周四表示，在长期粮食短缺和经济不平等加剧的情况下，朝鲜领导人金正恩呼吁在全国范围内建设工厂，在农村地区进行“工业革命”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:45:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-seeks-industry-revolution-rural-areas-amid-widening-inequality-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车和小鹏汽车称首款合资汽车将是电动SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-xpeng-ink-deal-develop-two-b-class-battery-evs-2024-02-29/</link><description>德国汽车制造商大众汽车和中国电动汽车 (EV) 合作伙伴小鹏汽车周四表示，他们计划合作开发的第一款汽车将是一款 SUV，并将为其联合采购零部件。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:29:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-xpeng-ink-deal-develop-two-b-class-battery-evs-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>商务部长表示中方愿加强与埃及的经贸合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-enhance-economic-trade-cooperation-with-egypt-commerce-minister-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国商务部援引中国商务部部长的话说，中方愿进一步促进与埃及的经贸合作，继续鼓励和支持中国企业赴埃投资兴业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 23:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-enhance-economic-trade-cooperation-with-egypt-commerce-minister-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>论文称加拿大因与北京分享信息而解雇了两名科学家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-fired-two-scientists-sharing-information-with-beijing-says-paper-2024-02-28/</link><description>据《环球邮报》周三报道，加拿大于 2021 年解雇了两名在高度安全的传染病实验室工作的科学家，因为他们向中国提供了机密信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 22:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-fired-two-scientists-sharing-information-with-beijing-says-paper-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：聚光灯聚焦日本、澳大利亚消费者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-28/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>北京将举办2027年世锦赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/beijing-host-2027-world-championships-2024-02-28/</link><description>世界田径管理机构周三表示，北京已被选为举办 2027 年世界田径锦标赛。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 20:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/beijing-host-2027-world-championships-2024-02-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>